<paragraph blockId="25.[189,1399,683,899]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
This species was described based on a single male specimen collected in Maroni, 
<collectingCountry box="[1213,1395,683,709]" name="French Guiana" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
. According to the original description, the specimen belonged to the Queensland Museum and was sent to Cockerell by Le Moult. Eugène Le Moult (
<date box="[744,879,759,786]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" value="1882" valueMax="1967">1882–1967</date>
) was a French naturalist and entomologist specialist on butterflies who lived in 
<collectingCountry box="[610,782,797,823]" name="French Guiana" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">French Guiana</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Lhoste" box="[795,945,797,823]" firstAuthor="Lhoste" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" refId="ref21109" refString="Lhoste J. 1987. Les Entomologistes francais. 1750 - 1950. Institut national de la Recherche agronomique, Paris." type="book" year="1987">Lhoste 1987</bibRefCitation>
). The 
<typeStatus box="[1014,1117,797,823]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">holotype</typeStatus>
is housed at 
<collectionCode box="[1261,1351,797,823]" country="USA" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34925" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34925" name="American Museum of Natural History" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">AMNH</collectionCode>
and has the following data label: 
<collectingCountry box="[536,630,835,861]" name="French Guiana" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Guyane</collectingCountry>
, Maroni. [printed]\ 
<taxonomicName authority="Ckll." authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1917" box="[866,1155,835,861]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="maroniana">
<emphasis box="[866,1089,835,861]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Centris maroniana</emphasis>
Ckll.
</taxonomicName>
Type [handwritten]\ ac33337 [handwritten]\ 
<collectionCode box="[469,559,873,899]" country="USA" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34925" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34925" name="American Museum of Natural History" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">AMNH</collectionCode>
_IZC 00323439 [data matrix code] [printed].
</paragraph>
