<paragraph blockId="25.[189,1399,1183,1248]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">
This is one of the most stunning species of the subgenus 
<emphasis box="[864,891,1183,1209]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">C.</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[909,1078,1183,1209]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">Melanocentris</emphasis>
). Unfortunately, nothing is known about its bionomy and distributional range.
</paragraph>
